message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product which is tailored to meet your specific needs. Given its value to you, I believe it's worth every penny. Considering its high quality and the benefits it offers, I am offering it to you for $14000. This price reflects both the value it holds for you and the opportunity to secure such a valuable asset at a competitive rate. Please let me know if this offer meets your expectations or if you have any further questions.
